OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fsecures settlement from    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fholiday park               
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A man groomed by paedophile Barry      
OL,6, Bennell while on holiday at Butlin's   
OL,7, has secured a five-figure settlement   
OL,8, from the company's previous owners.    
OL,10,FThe former football coach groomed David
OL,11,FLean, 52, after meeting him at the     
OL,12,FPwllheli resort, in Gwynedd, in 1979.  
OL,14,FMr Lean, who was 11 at the time, said  
OL,15,FBennell had "worked his charm" on him  
OL,16,Fand his father.                        
OL,18,FA spokesman for Hard Rock Cafe Limited,
OL,19,Fwhich owned Butlin's at the time,      
OL,20,Fdeclined to comment.                   
